<!-- Definition and medical uses -->
'''芐青黴素'''，或稱'''青黴素G'''，（{{lang-en|Benzylpenicillin}} 或 {{lang-en|penicillin G}}），是一種[[抗细菌药|抗生素]]，常用於治療[[病原细菌|細菌性]][[感染|感染]]，如[[肺炎|肺炎]]、[[鏈球菌性咽炎|鏈球菌性咽炎]]、[[梅毒|梅毒]]、[[壞死性小腸結腸炎|壞死性小腸結腸炎]]、[[白喉|白喉]]、{{tsl|en|gas gangrene|氣性壞疽}}、[[鉤端螺旋體病|鉤端螺旋體病]]、[[蜂窩組織炎|蜂窩組織炎]]和[[破傷風|破傷風]]<ref name=WHO2008/>。本品並非{{tsl|en|Pneumococcal infection|鏈球菌性感染|鏈球菌性}}[[腦膜炎|腦膜炎]]的一線用藥<ref name=WHO2008/>。芐青黴素的給藥方式為[[靜脈注射|靜脈注射]]或[[肌肉注射|肌肉注射]]<ref name=Pro2016>{{cite web|title=Penicillin G Injection - FDA prescribing information, side effects and uses|url=https://www.drugs.com/pro/penicillin-g-injection.html|website=www.drugs.com|access-date=2016-12-10|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220230501/https://www.drugs.com/pro/penicillin-g-injection.html|archive-date=2016-12-20}}</ref>。長效劑型現有{{le|苄乙二胺青黴素|benzathine benzylpenicillin}}和{{le|普卡因基青黴素|procaine benzylpenicillin}}兩種，給藥方式皆為肌肉注射<ref name=WHO2008/>。

<!-- Side effects and mechanism -->
副作用為[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]、[[癲癇發作|癲癇發作]]和[[過敏|過敏]]，甚至是[[過敏性休克|過敏性休克]]<ref name=WHO2008/>。當使用本品治療梅毒時，可能會發生[[雅-赫氏反應|雅-赫氏反應]]<ref name=WHO2008/>。如果患者有[[青黴素#不良反应|青黴素]]過敏紀錄，則不建議使用<ref name=WHO2008/>；但用於[[妊娠|懷孕]]患者應該是安全的<ref name=Pro2016/>。本品屬於[[青黴素|青黴素]]和[[Β-内酰胺|β-內醯胺]]類藥物<ref name=WHO2008>{{cite book | title = WHO Model Formulary 2008 | year = 2009 | isbn = 9789241547659 | vauthors = ((World Health Organization)) | veditors = Stuart MC, Kouimtzi M, Hill SR | hdl = 10665/44053 | author-link = World Health Organization | publisher = World Health Organization | hdl-access=free |pages=98, 105 }}</ref>。

<!-- Society and culture -->
1929年，[[亚历山大·弗莱明|亞歷山大·佛萊明]]發現了苄青黴素，1942年，開始商業化量產<ref>{{cite book|last1=Fischer|first1=Janos|last2=Ganellin|first2=C. Robin | name-list-format = vanc |title=Analogue-based Drug Discovery|date=2006|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9783527607495|page=490|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=FjKfqkaKkAAC&pg=PA490|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220081307/https://books.google.ca/books?id=FjKfqkaKkAAC&pg=PA490|archive-date=2016-12-20}}</ref>。本品名列於[[世界衛生組織基本藥物標準清單|世界衛生組織基本藥物標準清單]]中，認可為[[醫療系統|醫療系統]]中最安全有效的必需藥物之一<ref name="WHO21st">{{cite book | vauthors = ((World Health Organization)) | title = World Health Organization model list of essential medicines: 21st list 2019 | year = 2019 | hdl = 10665/325771 | author-link = World Health Organization | publisher = World Health Organization | location = Geneva | id = WHO/MVP/EMP/IAU/2019.06. License: CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 IGO | hdl-access=free }}</ref>。[[發展中國家|發展中國家]]的單日劑量批發價為0.24到2.72美金<ref name=ERC2014>{{cite web|title=Penicillin, Benzyl|url=http://mshpriceguide.org/en/single-drug-information/?DMFId=599&searchYear=2014|website=International Drug Price Indicator Guide|access-date=2016-12-08|archive-date=2018-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181013014327/http://mshpriceguide.org/en/single-drug-information/?DMFId=599&searchYear=2014|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然而在美國，整套療程藥劑則要價100到200 美金<ref name=Ric2015>{{cite book |last1=Hamilton |first1=Richart | name-list-format = vanc |title=Tarascon Pocket Pharmacopoeia 2015 Deluxe Lab-Coat Edition|date=2015|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|isbn=9781284057560|page=95}}</ref>。
